        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How do I add money to my UniCoins wallet?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                You can add money to your UniCoins wallet through the following methods:
                <ul>
                    <li>Online payment via the UniCoins app using your debit/credit card or UPI.</li>
                    <li>Cash top-up at designated UniCoins kiosks located on campus.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How are UniCoins credited after a payment?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                UniCoins are automatically credited to your wallet immediately after a successful payment at any participating vendor. You will receive a notification in the UniCoins app confirming the transaction and coin credit.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How many UniCoins do I earn per transaction?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                You earn 5 UniCoins for every 50 Rupees spent at participating vendors.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Where can I redeem my UniCoins?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                You can redeem your UniCoins at the following partner vendors within Presidency University campus:
                <ul>
                    <li>Hatti Kaapi</li>
                    <li>Stationary Shop</li>
                    <li>Fresh Choice</li>
                    <li>Udaya Upahara</li>
                    <li>And more partner vendors coming soon!</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">How do I redeem my UniCoins at a vendor?</div>
            <div class="faq-answer">
                Simply inform the vendor that you wish to redeem UniCoins during your purchase. The vendor will process the redemption through the UniCoins system, and the corresponding amount will be deducted from your wallet.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
            <div class="faq-question">Is there an expiry date for UniCoins?</div>
